{"word":"G2922 - κριτήριον - kritḗrion - kree-tay'-ree-on - To judge","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κριτήριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kritḗrion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kree-tay'-ree-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">To judge</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"தீர்ப்பு, நியாயம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. the rule by which one judges"},{"paragraph":"2. the place where judgment is given"},{"paragraph":"3. the matter judged, thing to be decided, suit, case"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2923 - κριτής - kritḗs - kree-tace'/2923\">G2923</a>; a <i>rule</i> of judging (&ldquo;criterion&rdquo;), that is, (by implication) a <i>tribunal:</i> - to judge, judgment (seat).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1252/1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253/1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469/1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178/178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631/2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632/2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633/2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917/2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919/2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920/2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922/2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923/2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924/2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350/350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351/351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470/470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610/610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611/611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612/612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843/843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87/87\">G87</a>"}]}